- content_for :title, "Become a Dealer"

%section.main
  .container
    .dealer-program
      %h1 Become an Authorized Dealer
      %p Join the Original Fuzz dealer program and get access to dealer pricing, exclusive deals, free shipping, and swag for your store.
      .one
        %h2 Benefits
        %ul
          %li Access to exclusive dealer deals.
          %li Dealer pricing (lowest available).
          %li Free shipping with purchase of dealer product bundles (These are discounted bundles of guitar strap starter packs or bag/strap combo pack).
          %li Original Fuzz guitar store swag (display cases, stickers, signage, picks, and more!).
      .one
        %h2 Requirements
        %ol
          %li Fill out our #{ link_to 'online application', 'https://originalfuzz.wufoo.com/forms/authorized-dealer-application/'} form.
          %li Purchase at least one dealer product bundle.
          %li Order any item every 60 days to maintain your Authorized Dealer status.
          %li Active your account on our dealer website (we'll send you a link to set up your account after you've completed our #{ link_to 'online application', 'https://originalfuzz.wufoo.com/forms/authorized-dealer-application/'} form).
          %li Dealer pricing is only available to stores that purchase through our dealer website. We're happy to take orders over email or the phone, but you'll only be able to receive our standard wholesale pricing.
    .dealer-application
      %h2 Join Today
      %p Fill out our simple #{ link_to 'online application', 'https://originalfuzz.wufoo.com/forms/authorized-dealer-application/'} and get started today. An account rep will get back to your in 1-2 business days. 
      %p= link_to "Apply Now", "https://originalfuzz.wufoo.com/forms/authorized-dealer-application/", class: "btn btn-primary"